  "description": {
    "fr": "Inflige {magicalDamage:v}.\n\\---\nLorsqu'un de vos personnages est soigné : {PAvalue:pa} au coût de ce {%SPELLCOUNT}.\n\\---\nTant que ce {%SPELLCOUNT} est dans votre main\\_: Votre héros a {DRAINvalue:d1,percent,+}. Il gagne {DRAINvalue:d2,percent,+} lorsqu’un de vos compagnons meurt.\n\\---\n{%DestroyOnPlayed}",
    "en": "Does {magicalDamage:v}.\n\\---\nWhen one of your characters is healed: {PAvalue:pa} to the cost of this {%SPELLCOUNT}.\n\\---\nWhile this {%SPELLCOUNT} is in your hand: Your hero has {DRAINvalue:d1,percent,+}. They gain {DRAINvalue:d2,percent,+} when one of your companions dies.\n\\---\n{%DestroyOnPlayed}",
    "es": "Inflige {magicalDamage:v}.\n\\---\nCuando uno de tus personajes es curado: {PAvalue:pa} al coste de este {%SPELLCOUNT}.\n\\---\nMientras que este {%SPELLCOUNT} esté en tu mano: Tu héroe tiene {DRAINvalue:d1,percent,+}. Gana {DRAINvalue:d2,percent,+} cuando uno de tus compañeros muere.\n\\---\n{%DestroyOnPlayed}",
    "de": "Verursacht {magicalDamage:v}.\n\\---\nWenn einer deiner Charaktere geheilt wird: {PAvalue:pa} auf Kosten dieses {%SPELLCOUNT}s.\n\\---\nSolange sich dieser {%SPELLCOUNT} auf deiner Hand befindet: Dein Held hat {DRAINvalue:d1,percent,+}. Wenn einer deiner Begleiter stirbt, erhält er {DRAINvalue:d2,percent,+}.\n\\---\n{%DestroyOnPlayed}",
    "pt": "Inflige {magicalDamage:v}.\n\\---\nQuando um dos seus personagens é curado: {PAvalue:pa} ao custo do {%SPELLCOUNT}.\n\\---\nQuando o {%SPELLCOUNT} está na sua mão: Seu herói possui {DRAINvalue:d1,percent,+}. Ele ganha {DRAINvalue:d2,percent,+} quando um dos seus companheiros morre.\n\\---\n{%DestroyOnPlayed}"
